Projects

Paylancer

This a web application I am developing for a company I founded called Accessible Analytics LLC. The web app is essentially a search engine that allows freelancers to see valuable data about the market for their skills. Data is scraped from the Upwork.com website using Python, with the Scrapy and Splash packages, the largest freelancing site in the world analyzed and displayed to the end user through our front-end built in React in the form of intuitive visuals. Unfortunately, due to IP concers, the source code is not publicly available, and the product has not launched yet. However, please watch the video demo of the product to learn more.

Demo Landing Page

Sudoku Star

This is a program I made to solve Sudoku puzzles. It was developed in the Qt Creator development environment using C++. It is very fast and solves puzzles in a matter of only a few milliseconds. Watch the demo to see it in action!
